Name:           Efreet
Short Name:     efreet
Level Required: 10

Description:
  A burning humanoid from the Elemental Plane of Fire, the Efreet
  attacks with its Flame Sword and can burn flesh with its bare hands.

Commands:
  - summon efreet:  Summons it to you         (costs 50 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban efreet:     Banishes it               (costs 20 sp)
